Name:           gstreamer1-libav
Version:        1.19.3
Release:        8%{?dist}
Summary:        GStreamer 1.0 libav-based plug-ins
Group:          Applications/Multimedia
License:        LGPLv2+
URL:            http://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/
